comments: Sabonis (SAC) avoids making contact with Lillard's (POR) arm during the pass.
Winslow (POR) reaches in for the loose ball and marginal contact occurs with Fox's (SAC) arm.
Winslow (POR) and Sabonis (SAC) briefly engage and disengage in the post.
Sabonis (SAC) jumps in the air and lands before releasing the pass.
Fox (SAC) is moving laterally while attempting to defend Simons (POR) at midcourt and he is able to move through the marginal contact.
Davis (SAC) grazes Lillard's (POR) arm as he gathers the ball but does not affect his SQBR.
Hart (POR) establishes a screening position and does not deliver illegal contact to Barnes (SAC) as it occurs on the perimeter.
Fox (SAC) drives through Grant's (POR) space and dislodges him from his defensive position.
Lillard (POR) slips and falls during his drive to the basket and any contact by Davis (SAC) is marginal.
Kings (SAC) extends his leg out and makes intentional foot to ball contact.
Sabonis (SAC) initiates contact with Grant?s (POR) head during the layup attempt.
Simons (POR) legally contests Fox?s (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) initiates contact with Hart?s (POR) head during the layup attempt.
Fox (SAC) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Winslow (POR) legally contests Huerter's (SAC) shot attempt.
Winslow (POR) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Hart (POR) legally contests Huerter?s (SAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Grant (POR) places two hands on Fox (SAC) and the contact affects his SQBR.
Simons (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Huerter's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Davis (SAC) makes contact to Grant's (POR) arm and affects his ability to secure the ball.
